PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-2129, which authorized the Minister of Finance to make advances to the CANADA DEPOSIT INSURANCE CORPORATION out of the Consolidated Revenue Fund, EXTENDING THE EXPIRY DATE TO MARCH 31, 1995 in order to coincide with the Corporation's new year end.
